726331f-a.text:
Colfax St., west side, between Springfield Boulevard and Hollis Ave., showing in a set of three views the B. Alberson house of 1873. P. Vanserlaw was the owner in 1891. Geo. E. and krs. James Van Siclen were the owners in 1892 and 1923 respectively. This house is about
1050 ft. north of Springfield Boulevard.
1922
Views 2 and 31 April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
